都係環球性質。我當一日有一萬宗意外 咁但係新聞抽一/兩件黎報 有咩意思？"},{"pid":"9d59fd3c49e90953cddd22ed5372e7288f0559a9","tid":731260,"uid":33643,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"新聞價值<br />\n<br />\n異常性：愈不平常，愈有新聞價值；「異常性」有個廣為人知的例子：「狗咬人不是新聞, 人咬狗是新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n影響性：影響愈多人，愈有新聞價值<br />\n<br />\n及時性：愈即時發生的事，愈有新聞價值<br />\n<br />\n地域性：愈貼近聽眾或讀者的生活領域，愈有新聞價值<br />\n<br />\n顯著性：愈出名的人事，愈有新聞價值<br />\n<br />\n衝突性：愈有衝突元素，愈有新聞價值"},{"pid":"e8b564380cea56ccf63cdd722a74cff2d9b1fa16","tid":731260,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"News values, <br />\nsometimes called news criteria, determine how much prominence a news story is given by a media outlet, and the attention it is given by the audience. They explain how editors and other journalists decide that one piece of information is news while another is not.<br />\n<br />\nMore:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-sDyJH2OieJk/TrR84shLxdI/AAAAAAAAAGE/EDYS4xukfDA/s1600/News+Values.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-sDyJH2OieJk%2FTrR84shLxdI%2FAAAAAAAAAGE%2FEDYS4xukfDA%2Fs1600%2FNews%2BValues.jpg&h=e59758bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a8bc1a33ab4bb1dc02485acb01a9cd47e1a0df5","tid":731260,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ebb80278804fd1e49ae8db18fe9beb59ab634e8","tid":731260,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf3cd7885668ea68138eb0157ab33cfb910e336","tid":731260,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36148c4a8440a213fcf8d49bd9b9ed14f109d6ff","tid":731260,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"例如每日都有好多人死亡<br />\n點解只有少數意外成份高嘅 可以獲得關注？而因其他原因死亡嘅就唔係新聞？<br />\n每日咁多交通意外，點解又要抽幾單出黎播？<br />\n<br />\n感覺上係完全無內容<br />\n究竟係點樣設計？呢啲野有咩價值？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"你都識講意外，自然死就唔會報啦<br />\n有死傷/炒得嚴重咪會報<br />\n當然主要係睇電視台有無派人出去影，拍左d片&